  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>This hotel provides a continental buffet breakfast with additional hot options including a range of meats and cheeses, cakes, pastries and fruits, served between 6:30 - 10:30am. Dinner is a three course a la carte evening meal with choice of menu and is served between 7:00 - 9:00pm. Please note that it may be necessary to book your time slot for dinner during check in. </p>
<p>Christmas and New Year gala dinner included, and guests have the option for earlier mealtimes for children (available on request).</p>
<p>There's an amazing opportunity to dine around Chamonix with a choice of restaurants, that's included in the half board. Guests can try both the 'Brasserie I'M', which is a long standing and well known brasserie in the centre of the resort, and the 'Hotel Lykke' restaurants once per week, where an equivalent meal to the half board dinner will be provided.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
