  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Twin rooms </strong>are around 22m² and sleep two people with a balcony with Mont Blanc views (available for sole occupancy, on request).</p>
<p><strong>Triple rooms</strong> are around 25m² and sleep three people. There can be either 3 single beds or a double with an additional single bed. There's a balcony with Aiguilles de Chamonix East facing mountain views.</p>
<p><strong>Bedroom facilities</strong></p>
